NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BHoward Schutzman: ^*N|cp||at|On the other hand, NT is vastly overrated by most players who play Match Points. Yes, sometimes you can make the same number of tricks in NT and a suit. But quite often you can take one more trick in a suit than in NT. And, when you bid slam, you rate to get an average plus board regardless.|
